  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What you read and what is a difference in what you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I can't blame him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This-- what hurts me today, that this patriotism, what it was when arrived to Israel, is not anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only one message.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whenever you have a chance to talk, and mostly to non-Jews, tell them what happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And tell them that all these books what Germany already coming out, denying the whole story, that we fabricated this phony story, tell them it's not true.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the whole idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "More, I cannot tell them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I hope never again, in the future, would happen such a barbaric, nasty, dirty things, what happened in the past.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is, I think, the worst history, the worst thing get what was done to human being.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe if the world would look up a little bit and start to learn, from this, something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When they took 1 and 1/2 million Romanians, the Turkish people, first World War, and the whole world forgot about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they will do, this time something, maybe, about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it wouldn't get to this point, that, this should happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the Jews should never trust the Arabs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there's nothing to trust them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have only one plan, to take over this little world from the map, Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the only plan was as Arafat, and the rest of their Arabs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
